test_list_of_zeros:
assert [0, 0, 0, 0] == [0, 0, 0]
  Left contains one more item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0, 0]
  + [0, 0, 0, 0]
  ?        +++
test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [9, 9, 9, 9] == [9, 9, 9]
  Left contains one more item: 9
  Full diff:
  - [9, 9, 9]
  + [9, 9, 9, 9]
  ?        +++
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [-54, -63, -72] == [-63, -72]
  At index 0 diff: -54 != -63
  Left contains one more item: -72
  Full diff:
  - [-63, -72]
  + [-54, -63, -72]
  ?  +++++
